# Backend FastAPI โ€” Patterns et conventions

## Stack

- Python 3.12 via **uv**
- FastAPI (async)
- SQLAlchemy 2 (async, asyncpg)
- PostgreSQL 15 (Docker)
- Alembic (migrations)
- Pydantic v2 (validation)
- PyJWT + bcrypt (auth)

## Commandes courantes

```bash
